history.content:
CS170 will be having an AUA (Ask Us Anything) session this Tuesday May 5th! We will have TA panelists from 2:15-3pm and then professors Alessandro and Jelani from 3-3:45pm (all times PDT and starting at specified time, not Berkeley time). Zoom link: https://berkeley.zoom.us/j/95783314351.

This is a open to all students (i.e. you do not need to have taken 170 to join) and is a great opportunity to ask questions to experienced TAs/Readers, graduating seniors, and professors!

Small disclaimer: Just because this is AUA does not mean we can or need to answer everything.
